.TH ENGLISH-CALC 1 "November 2025" "english-calc 1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
english-calc \- simple English calculator for arithmetic expressions
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B english-calc
.RI " expression" ""
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B english-calc
command evaluates short English arithmetic phrases like "three plus five"
or numeric expressions like "3 plus 5" and prints the result.

Supported operators: plus, minus, times, divided

Examples:
.RS 4
.TP
english-calc three plus five
.TP
english-calc 4 times 6
.RE
